author: The Jersey Journal
title: Bayonne estate sale Saturday to benefit Hudson County Animal League
text: The heiress, whose identity is being kept confidential, is a devoted volunteer for HCAL, and has vowed that whatever her share of the proceeds from the sale may be, it will all go to HCAL to support their efforts to provide shelter, medical care and adoption services to homeless animals throughout Hudson County.
